            "title": "極兔速遞首季包裹量按年增長31.2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">極兔速遞(01519)公布，今年首季包裹量達66億件，按年增長31.2%；日均包裹量7330萬件，按年更升32.6%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：極兔速遞官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_01519-3-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：極兔速遞官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_01519-3-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：極兔速遞官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內以東南亞地區包裹量增長最多，首季處理15.38億件，按年升50%，日均包裹量1710萬件，增長51.6%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國包裹量所佔比例依然最大，首季包裹量達49.85億件，按年增長26.5%；日均包裹量5540萬件，增27.9%。新市場包裹量7660萬件，按年升19.4%；日均包裹量85萬件，增長20.8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14843174-%e6%a5%b5%e5%85%94%e9%80%9f%e9%81%9e%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e5%8c%85%e8%a3%b9%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b731-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241010_FI_source-web_01519-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 08:55:38",
